Name: Pancakes

@Egg{3%pcs}
@Flour{125%grams}
@Milk{250%ml}
@Butter{50%grams}
@Salt{1%pinch}

#Bowl
#Whisk
#Pan

Mix the @Egg{3%pcs}, @Flour{125%grams}, @Milk{250%ml}, @Butter{50%grams}, and @Salt{1%pinch} in a #Bowl using a #Whisk until smooth.

Heat a #Pan over medium heat for ~{2%minutes}.

Pour a ladle of the batter into the #Pan and tilt to spread evenly.

Cook for ~{2%minutes} on one side, then flip and cook for ~{1%minute} on the other side.

Serve immediately with your favorite topping.